# Project Conventions

## Tech Stack

- React 19, TypeScript, Vite (rolldown-vite)
- TanStack Router (file-based routing with hash history)
- Tailwind CSS 4, Base UI (via basecn)
- pnpm package manager

## File Structure

- `src/routes/` - TanStack Router file-based routes
- `src/components/ui/` - Base UI components (basecn)
- `src/components/layout/` - Layout components (TopNav, Sidebar)
- `src/lib/` - Utilities and helpers

## Code Style

- Prettier for formatting (run `pnpm format`)
- Single quotes, trailing commas, 100 char line width
- Type-only imports: `import { type Foo }` or `import type { Foo }`

## Commands

- `pnpm dev` - Start dev server
- `pnpm build` - Build for production
- `pnpm typecheck` - Check TypeScript errors
- `pnpm format` - Format code with Prettier

## Theme

- CSS variables in `src/index.css`
- Red primary color, neutral sidebar
- Dark/light mode via ThemeContext
